{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d6b008b4d1","title":"转发河北省委关于沧县地委镇反工作经验的通报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3392cc2c12","index":0,"year":1951,"month":3,"day":23,"articleId":"d6b008b4d1"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"e087f092cc","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d6b008b4d1","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共河北省委1951年3月14日通报中介绍的沧县地委镇反工作的主要经验是：一、广泛深入教育干部和党员，明确故我界限，在党内以批评自我批评的武器开展斗争，统一思想。二、召开县的人民代表会议，贯彻镇压反革命的精神，通过代表将镇压反革命的精神贯彻到群众中去。三、广泛开展镇压反革命的宣传工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"69e446fb21","type":"title","text":"转发河北省委关于沧县地委镇反工作经验的通报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d6b008b4d1"},{"id":"e087f092cc","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，各大军区党委，志司，并转分局，省委，大中市委，区党委，省军区及地委同志们","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d6b008b4d1"},{"id":"492a7a36a9","type":"paragraph","text":"这是沧县地委的镇反经验”，请你们发给所有中央局委员，大车区委员，分局委员，省委区党委委员，省军区委员，大中市委委员，大中市委所属区委书记，每人一份，并请每人看一遍，至要至盼。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d6b008b4d1"},{"id":"ab3eec99f4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d6b008b4d1"},{"id":"2f9781f929","type":"paragraph","text":"三月二十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d6b008b4d1"}],"page":{"id":"91548479cc","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d6b008b4d1","start":183,"end":183}}}},"__N_SSG":true}